'''2017年土庫曼總統選舉'''在2017年2月12日舉行<ref>[https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/turkmenistan-sets-presidential-election-for-2017/2016/10/16/50f4aa9a-93ae-11e6-9cae-2a3574e296a6_story.html Turkmenistan sets presidential election for 2017] {{Wayback|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/asia_pacific/turkmenistan-sets-presidential-election-for-2017/2016/10/16/50f4aa9a-93ae-11e6-9cae-2a3574e296a6_story.html |date=20161114084235 }} Washington Post, 16 October 2016</ref>，自2007年起任總統的[[庫爾班古力·別爾德穆哈梅多夫|庫爾班古力·別爾德穆哈梅多夫]]爭取第3度連任，最終以97.69%的得票率成功連任。

==背景==
2016年9月，[[土库曼斯坦宪法|土库曼斯坦宪法]]作出修訂，刪除總統候選人任期限制和70歲的年齡限制，並將總統任期從五年延長到七年<ref>[http://thediplomat.com/2016/09/constitutional-changes-pave-way-for-turkmen-president-for-life/ Constitutional Changes Pave Way for Turkmen President-for-Life] {{Wayback|url=http://thediplomat.com/2016/09/constitutional-changes-pave-way-for-turkmen-president-for-life/ |date=20161117105209 }} The Diplomat, 16 September 2016</ref>。

==選舉制度==
[[土库曼斯坦总统|土库曼斯坦总统]]採用[[两轮选举制|两轮选举制]]選出<ref>[http://www.electionguide.org/elections/id/2223/ Turkmenistan] {{Wayback|url=http://www.electionguide.org/elections/id/2223/ |date=20181004053531 }} IFES</ref>。

==候選人==
截至2016年12月，時任總統[[库尔班古力·别尔德穆哈梅多夫|库尔班古力·别尔德穆哈梅多夫]]獲得[[土庫曼斯坦民主黨|土庫曼斯坦民主黨]]的提名；另有八位候選人已獲中央選舉委員會批准參選<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.azernews.az/region/107090.html|title=Turkmen presidential candidates start campaigning|date=2016-12-29|newspaper=AzerNews.az|language=en-US|access-date=2016-12-29|archive-date=2016-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161229172715/http://www.azernews.az/region/107090.html|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.rferl.org/a/nine-candidates-run-turkmenistan-presidential-election/28201082.html|title=Nine Candidates Register To Run In Turkmenistan's Presidential Election|website=RadioFreeEurope/RadioLiberty|access-date=2016-12-29|archive-date=2016-12-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161229104748/http://www.rferl.org/a/nine-candidates-run-turkmenistan-presidential-election/28201082.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

